        console.log("manage_vwo_consent_state loaded in the footer");

        // Initialize VWO with default consent management setup
        window.VWO = window.VWO || [];
        window.VWO.init = window.VWO.init || function(state) {
            window.VWO.consentState = state;
            console.log("VWO consent state set to:", state);
        };

        // Function to check and parse the tracking-preferences cookie
        function updateVWOConsent() {
            console.log("Checking for tracking-preferences cookie...");
            console.log("All cookies:", document.cookie); // Log all cookies for clarity

            // Locate the 'tracking-preferences' cookie
            var consentCookie = document.cookie.split("; ").find(function(row) {
                return row.startsWith("tracking-preferences=");
            });

            if (consentCookie) {
                console.log("Consent cookie found:", consentCookie);

                try {
                    // Decode and parse the cookie value
                    var consentValue = consentCookie.split("=")[1];
                    var decodedConsentValue = decodeURIComponent(consentValue);
                    console.log("Decoded consent value:", decodedConsentValue);

                    var consentData = JSON.parse(decodedConsentValue);
                    console.log("Parsed consent data:", consentData);

                    // Check the marketing and analytics consent explicitly
                    if (consentData.custom && consentData.custom.marketingAndAnalytics === true) {
                        console.log("Marketing and analytics consent detected as true.");
                        window.VWO.init(1); // Accepted
                    } else {
                        console.log("Marketing and analytics consent detected as false or undefined.");
                        window.VWO.init(3); // Denied
                    }
                    // Clear the interval once consent is set to avoid repeated checks
                    clearInterval(consentCheckInterval);
                } catch (error) {
                    console.error("Error parsing consent data:", error);
                }
            } else {
                console.log("Consent cookie not found yet; consent state remains Pending.");
                window.VWO.init(2); // Pending
            }
        }

        // Re-check every 5 seconds until consent cookie is set
        var consentCheckInterval = setInterval(updateVWOConsent, 5000);
    </script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
        console.log("🔄 Loading Arcade tracking script...");

        /**
         * ✅ Define `triggerVWOEvent` in the global scope
         */
        window.triggerVWOEvent = function(interactionType) {
            console.log(`🛠 Attempting to trigger VWO event for: ${interactionType}`);

            function checkVWO(attempts = 10) {
                if (window.VWO && typeof VWO.event === "function" && VWO.state === "executionComplete") {
                    VWO.event("arcadeVideoPlay", {
                        interactionType: interactionType,
                        pageURL: window.location.href
                    });
                    console.log(`✅ VWO event 'arcadeVideoPlay' triggered successfully for: ${interactionType}`);
                } else if (attempts > 0) {
                    console.warn(`⏳ VWO still loading. Retrying in 1 sec... (${attempts} attempts left)`);
                    setTimeout(() => checkVWO(attempts - 1), 1000);
                } else {
                    console.error("❌ VWO event not fired after multiple attempts. State:", VWO.state);
                }
            }
            checkVWO();
        };

        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
            console.log("✅ Arcade tracking script loaded.");
            var arcadeIframe = document.getElementById("arcadeIframe");

            if (arcadeIframe) {
                console.log("✅ Arcade iframe found. Listening for Arcade interactions...");

                const allowedOrigin = "https://demo.arcade.software";

                window.addEventListener("message", function (event) {
                    console.log("📩 Full message event received:", event);

                    if (event.origin !== allowedOrigin) {
                        console.warn("❌ Ignoring event from untrusted origin:", event.origin);
                        return;
                    }

                    if (!event.data) {
                        console.warn("⚠️ No data found in message event.");
                        return;
                    }

                    console.log("📩 Message data:", event.data);

                    if (!event.data.eventName) {
                        console.warn("⚠️ No eventName found in event data:", event.data);
                        return;
                    }

                    console.log("✅ Arcade interaction detected:", event.data.eventName);
                    triggerVWOEvent(event.data.eventName);
                });
            } else {
                console.error("❌ Arcade iframe NOT found.");
            }
        });
    </script>
